
  Poliwhirl    Water Type Pokémon

  Capable of living in or out 
  of water.  When out of water, 
  it sweats to keep its body slimy. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Poliwag ► Poliwhirl ► Poliwrath

 Stage 3 Forms:
  poliwrath
  politoed

